{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-14531/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-14531"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:45:31"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man stares out at a crowd."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14531/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-14531","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14531/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-14531"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14531/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14531/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14531/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14531/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14531/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14531/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14531/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14531/canvas/1/af9a3f48-1893-4a91-9958-d045e91fe210","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-02T20:07:51.948Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>When Reynolds spots Alma in the crowd, a spotlight falls on his face. This is a complicated moment in the film (one of many). He finally sees Alma on her own, in her element, enjoying life as she wants to and appears to appreciate this sight. Much of the film’s tension revolves around this inability of characters (particularly Reynolds) to see from another’s perspective. The carnivalesque atmosphere of the New Year’s Eve party breaks down these barriers and, at least momentarily, allows Reynolds to see Alma beyond his standard gaze and outside the framework of his aesthetics. Nonetheless, when a fight breaks out, he will swoop down to collect his muse and creation and take her home.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14531/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:659.0445859872611,100.6454020700636,752.2541799363053,801.6565485668789"}}}]}]}]}